Two routers connecting via wan and with two lans. Setup a SECURE
tunnel between the two lans.
┌─────────┐               ┌─────────┐
│         │               │         │
│   PC1   │               │   PC2   │
│         │               │         │
└───eth0──┘               └───eth0──┘
 .100│                     .100│
     │lanA                     │lanB
     │192.168.1.0/24           │192.168.2.0/24
   .1│                       .1│
┌───eth1──┐               ┌───eth1──┐
│         │     wan       │         │
│   R1   eth0───────────eth0   R2   │
│         │ 100.60.10.0/16│         │
└─────────┘               └─────────┘
     .1                        .2

Setup the secure ip tunnel between r1 and r2 using openvpn
and enable the use of the tunnel when connecting the traffic between
the two lans.
